text:
Very fresh fried, crispy outside and mushy inside.
Chicken chop is good. Sauce is great 😋
coleslaw salad is delicious and fresh

Good price and portion.

Nice Home Based Burger Stall

Cleanliness:⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
Waiting time:⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Food: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Homebased Burger Stall at Kota Iskandar, Iskandar Puteri, Gelang Patah, (Tanjung Kupang)

You should try their chiken chop, it served with nice homemade blackpaper sauce.

Then relax your self with a cup of Flavored Coffe. Sure will bring you up to other level.

They also serve Nice Street Burger. You should try.

Welcome to Gelang Patah
